{"slug":"sirkuler-24-0739eng-1","reference":"Sirkuler_24_0739ENG","gazette":"Official Gazette No. 32675, dated 27 September 2024","title":"Anti-dumping measures on solar panels originating from Croatia, Malaysia, Thailand, Jordan and Vietnam converted into definitive measures","date":"28 Eylül 2024","bodyHtml":"<p>Following the completion of the investigation against the ineffectiveness of the measures initiated by the General Directorate of Imports of the Ministry of Trade against the import of goods defined as “photovoltaic cells combined into a module or arranged in panels” (solar panels) under the customs tariff statistical position 8541.43.00.00.00 originating in/from the Republic of Croatia, Malaysia, the Kingdom of Thailand, the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan and the Socialist Republic of Vietnam, it was decided to collect the anti-dumping measure applied in the form of a guarantee.</p><p>After 26.03.2024,&nbsp; a deposit of 25 USD/m2&nbsp; &nbsp; was required for the relevant goods.<br></p><p>As a result of the investigation, it was decided that the anti-dumping measure in force on imports originating from the PRC within the scope of the Communiqué on Prevention of Unfair Competition in Imports (Communiqué No: 2023/26) will be applied to imports originating from/exiting Croatia, Malaysia , Thailand, Jordan and Vietnam, with the exception of goods manufactured by Jinko Solar Technology Sdn. Bhd. established in Malaysia, Vina Solar Technology Company Limited, JA Solar Vietnam Company Limited and Trina Solar Energy Development Company Limited established in Vietnam and Trina Solar Science &amp; Technology (Thailand) Ltd. established in Thailand, as shown in the table.<br></p><p><a href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2024/09/20240927-7.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">Click here for the Communiqué on Prevention of Unfair Competition in Imports (No: 2024/30).</font></a><br></p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"caption-side: bottom; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; border: none; outline: 0px !important;\"><tbody style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; outline: 0px !important;\"><tr style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; outline: 0px !important;\"><td width=\"104\" style=\"border: 1pt solid windowtext; width: 77.75pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; line-height: 12pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><b style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: black; outline: 0px !important; font-weight: 400 !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">GTIP</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></b></p></td><td width=\"123\" style=\"border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: none; width: 92pt; border-image: initial; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; line-height: 12pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><b style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: black; outline: 0px !important; font-weight: 400 !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">Item Description</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></b></p></td><td width=\"85\" style=\"border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowte